additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: Always read the label and follow the directions for use. If symptoms persist, talk to your health professional. Contains benzoates, sorbates and sulfites. Advise your doctor of any medicine you take during pregnancy, particularly in your first trimester. If you are concerned about the health of yourself or your baby, talk to your health practitioner. If you are taking other products for pregnancy, talk to your health proessional before using this product.
